status.name: status
status.description: The port status. Value is ACTIVE or DOWN.

admin_state.description: The administrative state of the router, which is up (true) or down (false).

security_groups.description: The IDs of any attached security groups.

device_id.description: The ID of the device that uses this port. For example, a virtual server.
